## Anti-patterns to avoid

- Generic "Welcome" or "Home" titles
- Missing meta descriptions
- Broken heading hierarchy
- Images without alt text
- Vague, non-descriptive links ("click here", "learn more")
- Duplicate content without canonical tags
- Indexing process/workflow pages (should be `noIndex: true`)
- English metadata in Polish application
